      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "Sole typeface across every context — nav, body, headings, links, footer. The deliberate choice of a single weight at 400 across all roles removes typographic hierarchy and forces the grid and the imagery to do the ranking. No display cuts, no bold emphasis, no italics — restraint as a point of view."
    }
